{"ID":"20260605150132-14wr1xm","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605150132-14wr1xm","title":"2021年新高考Ⅱ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605150225"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605150147-pyei40p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150147-pyei40p","updated":"20260605150147"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示儿子"}]},{"ID":"20260605150147-0hrzo8v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150147-0hrzo8v","updated":"20260605150147"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陆游"}]},{"ID":"20260605150147-g9kebgt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150147-g9kebgt","updated":"20260605150147"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"禄食无功我自知，汝曹何以报明时？"}]},{"ID":"20260605150147-5bc3u1c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150147-5bc3u1c","updated":"20260605150147"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为农为士亦奚异，事国事亲惟不欺。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150147-jr7wv70","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150147-jr7wv70","updated":"20260605150147"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道在六经宁有尽，躬耕百亩可无饥。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150147-6sqlsw1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150147-6sqlsw1","updated":"20260605150147"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最亲切处今相付，热读周公七月诗。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150153-a4nckcf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150153-a4nckcf","updated":"20260605150153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【注】七月诗：指《诗经·风·七月》，是一首描写农民劳作和生活的农事诗。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150132-vshuguy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605150132-vshuguy","updated":"20260605150202"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605150202-rkz2fsq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150202-rkz2fsq","updated":"20260605150202"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．下列对这首诗的理解和赏析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605150202-h9h9oug","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150202-h9h9oug","updated":"20260605150202"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．本诗的首联以问句领起全篇，自然引出下文诗人对儿子的谆谆教诲。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150202-5bxoy1b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150202-5bxoy1b","updated":"20260605150202"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．诗人指出，不论是侍奉父母还是服务国家，“不欺”都是至关重要的。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150202-2xeij9q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150202-2xeij9q","updated":"20260605150202"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．诗人认为，生逢“明时”不必读书求仕，“躬耕”才是一种理想状态。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150202-5pc288p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150202-5pc288p","updated":"20260605150202"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．诗人在最后强调，自己传授给儿子的人生道理是最为真切、确实的。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150202-rn4tz36","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150202-rn4tz36","updated":"20260605150202"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．诗人指出“道在六经宁有尽”，又让儿子“熟读周公七月诗”，对此你是如何理解的？"}]},{"ID":"20260605150132-mweu5zh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605150132-mweu5zh","updated":"20260605150212"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605150132-gnofqpy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150132-gnofqpy","updated":"20260605150212"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．C    16．诗人借助这两句对子孙提出要求：诗书无涯，发奋读书；法乎先圣，修身立事；心怀家国，永存社稷。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150132-5rdsxuf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605150132-5rdsxuf","updated":"20260605150225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605150225-w34l25s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150225-w34l25s","updated":"20260605150225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．本题考查学生理解赏析诗歌内容的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150225-e3ckf3s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150225-e3ckf3s","updated":"20260605150225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“诗人认为，生逢‘明时’不必读书求仕，‘躬耕’才是一种理想状态”错误，由颔联“为农为士亦奚异，事国事亲惟不欺”可知，作者认为无论是出仕朝廷，为官一方，还是成为平民百姓，躬耕陇亩，都要事国以忠，事亲以孝，并没有在两种方式中做出比较选择。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150225-j1ozxhw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150225-j1ozxhw","updated":"20260605150225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150225-c9u04bv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150225-c9u04bv","updated":"20260605150225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．本题考查学生评价作者的情态和态度的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150225-pfcc8p5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150225-pfcc8p5","updated":"20260605150225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从题干来看，考生要理解“诗人指出‘道在六经宁有尽’”，又让儿子‘熟读周公七月诗’”的用意。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150225-ophybfe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150225-ophybfe","updated":"20260605150225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先分析诗歌的标题。诗歌标题是“示儿子”，可见这是一首教导儿子的诗歌。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150225-rv2g2k6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150225-rv2g2k6","updated":"20260605150225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"然后理解题干中两句诗的意思，进一步分析诗人这样的用意。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150225-203i12s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150225-203i12s","updated":"20260605150225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“道在六经宁有尽”意思是“天下大道，都在《六经》等书里，学贯古今，取法先圣，学习知识，哪里有尽头”，诗人在此指出《六经》的意义，包含天下大道，这是要求儿孙能够熟读《六经》，发奋阅读，“宁有尽”是说没有尽头，这是让儿孙不能停止不前，这是让儿孙不要自满，要谦虚以待。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150225-0gwar6n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150225-0gwar6n","updated":"20260605150225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“熟读周公七月诗”意思是“切记一定要熟记背诵周公的七月诗啊”，周公为国为家为民，鞠躬尽瘁，呕心沥血，诗人要求儿孙好好学习周公的七月诗，勤俭耕种，发奋读书，报效家国，这是让儿孙学习先圣，心怀国家。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150132-0qnb6cc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150132-0qnb6cc","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}